 style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;font-weight:bold;\"></span> </p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"> <span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;font-weight:bold;\">B、新员工试用期1-3个月，试用期工资为岗位工资的80%，转正之后，缴纳五险；</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;font-weight:bold;\"></span> </p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"> <span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;font-weight:bold;\">C、班次：月休4天；三班三倒、8小时工作制；</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;font-weight:bold;\"></span> </p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"> <span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;font-weight:bold;\">D、福利政策：免费住宿（4人宿舍，桌子、椅子、衣橱、宽带一应俱全）；现代化大型浴池；双职工宿舍；班车（每周一班：公司-东营-广饶）、生日蛋糕、结婚礼金、春节报销返程路费等；</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;font-weight:bold;\"></span> </p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"> <span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;font-weight:bold;\">E、公司职工餐厅菜品多样，价格便宜；</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;font-weight:bold;\"></span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;font-weight:bold;\">F、公司其它配套性设施良好，如篮球场、桌球室、乒乓球室等，能够最大限度的满足员工的个性需求；</span><span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;font-weight:bold;\"></span> </p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"> <span style=\"font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:12pt;font-weight:bold;\">乘车路线：从东营长途汽车总站乘车（东营至东营港）或东营-仙河-海港，途经爱克森公司门口（地址：山东省&nbsp;东营市&nbsp;东营港经济开发区&nbsp;海港路5号）。 </p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:15pt;font-weight:bold;\">联系方式：&nbsp;朱先生&nbsp;&nbsp; </p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:15pt;font-weight:bold;\">0546-8879891&nbsp; </p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;font-size:15pt;font-weight:bold;\">&nbsp;13954689895&nbsp;</span> </p> </span></span></span> <p> &nbsp; </p>
                    </dl>
                    
